      "role": "user",
      "content": "I don't really care about the 'airline gods' or any of that, I just need to get to Singapore. You mentioned obstacles and different paths though—can you actually look at the logistics? If I look at a route through Dubai, what are the specific things that usually cause the most delay in that connection compared to a direct flight from another hub like Paris or Frankfurt?",
